      "text": [
        "237 - وَبِإِسْنادِهِ قالَ: قالَ النَّبِي‏ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِوَآلِهِ: لا يَرى‏ عَوْرَتِي غَيْرِ عَلِيِّ إِلاّ كافِرٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.dr-ali-peiravi": [
          "31-237 According to the same documentation, the Prophet (S) said, “Should anyone but Ali (a.s.) look at my private parts he would be an atheist.”"
        ]
      }
    }
